demo_transcript:
{
  "messages": [
    {
      "user": "Whatfix Sales Person",
      "content": "Hello everyone, thank you for taking the time to join this demo call today. I'm excited to show you how Whatfix can help Marks and Spencer improve their employee training and onboarding processes, and ultimately reduce emissions throughout their value chain. Before we dive in, I just want to confirm that everyone is comfortable with the agenda we sent over prior to this call."
    },
    {
      "user": "Marks and Spencer's Representative",
      "content": "Yes, we're all set. We're looking forward to seeing how Whatfix can help us achieve our sustainability goals."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix Sales Person",
      "content": "Great. So, let's start with our Digital Adoption Platform. This is where you can create in-app guidance on any application that looks 100% native. Our no-code editor makes it easy to create customized guidance that fits your specific needs. Would you like me to show you how it works?"
    },
    {
      "user": "Marks and Spencer's Representative",
      "content": "Yes, please do."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix Sales Person",
      "content": "Okay. So, here's an example of how our Digital Adoption Platform can be used to provide personalized guidance to employees within a web application. As you can see, the guidance is contextual and interactive, making it easy for employees to learn and adopt new applications."
    },
    {
      "user": "Marks and Spencer's Representative",
      "content": "That's really impressive. How does it handle different languages? We have international customers and employees who need support in their native languages."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix Sales Person",
      "content": "Ah, great question. Our platform supports multiple languages, so you can provide personalized guidance to your international customers and employees in their native languages. We've had success with similar implementations with other clients who have global operations."
    },
    {
      "user": "Marks and Spencer's Representative",
      "content": "That's good to know. What about integration with our existing systems and applications? We have a lot of custom-built tools that we use."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix Sales Person",
      "content": "Our platform is highly customizable and can be integrated with a wide range of applications and systems. We've worked with clients who have complex systems and have been able to integrate our platform seamlessly. We can also provide customized integration support to ensure a smooth implementation."
    },
    {
      "user": "Marks and Spencer's Representative",
      "content": "Okay, that sounds promising. Can you show us some examples of how your platform can be used for employee training and onboarding?"
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix Sales Person",
      "content": "Absolutely. Our Employee Training and Onboarding feature provides personalized guidance and support to employees, making it easy for them to learn and adopt new applications. We've seen significant reductions in training time and costs with our clients who have implemented this feature. Let me show you an example..."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix Sales Person",
      "content": "As you can see, our platform provides a immersive and interactive experience for employees, making it easy for them to learn and adopt new applications. We've also seen significant increases in employee engagement and productivity with our clients who have implemented this feature."
    },
    {
      "user": "Marks and Spencer's Representative",
      "content": "That's really impressive. How do you measure the effectiveness of your platform? Can you provide some data or case studies on the impact it's had on other clients?"
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix Sales Person",
      "content": "Yes, of course. We have a number of case studies and success stories that demonstrate the impact our platform has had on our clients. For example, one of our clients in the retail industry saw a 30% reduction in training time and a 25% increase in employee productivity after implementing our platform. We also provide analytics and insights on application usage and user behavior, so you can optimize your training and support programs."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix Sales Person",
      "content": "Before we wrap up, I just want to confirm that you're comfortable with the features and functionality we've demonstrated today. Are there any other questions or concerns you have about our platform?"
    },
    {
      "user": "Marks and Spencer's Representative",
      "content": "No, I think that covers everything. We're interested in moving forward with the implementation. What are the next steps?"
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix Sales Person",
      "content": "Great. We'll send over a customized proposal outlining the implementation plan, timeline, and pricing. We'll also set up a follow-up call to answer any additional questions you may have. Sound good?"
    },
    {
      "user": "Marks and Spencer's Representative",
      "content": "Yes, sounds good. Thank you for the demo today."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix Sales Person",
      "content": "You're welcome. Thank you for considering Whatfix. We're looking forward to the opportunity to work with you."
    }
  ]
}

